name: Dainty Turquoise Hamsa Bracelet
description:
Add a pop of color and spirituality to your wrist stack. Our Dainty Turquoise Hamsa Bracelet is the perfect balance of subtlety and statement.

Handcrafted with a slender gold-filled chain, the centerpiece is a beautifully detailed Hamsa hand in striking turquoise. Whether worn alone for a clean, elegant look or layered with other gold chains, this bracelet is a versatile addition to any jewelry collection.

Features:

Material: High-quality Gold Filled chain.

Centerpiece: Turquoise Hamsa with Evil Eye detail.

Style: Minimalist, Boho-Chic.

Closure: Secure spring ring clasp.

name: Big Silver Leaves
description:
Inspired by the quiet elegance of nature, these handcrafted leaf earrings are made from solid sterling silver and carefully finished by hand.
Their delicate openwork design creates a light, airy feel while still making a statement — refined and feminine.
Each pair is individually crafted using traditional jewelry-making techniques, ensuring no two earrings are exactly alike.
Lightweight and comfortable, they move beautifully with you and catch the light in a subtle, elegant way.

Perfect for everyday wear or special occasions, these earrings add a natural sophistication to any outfit.
(number: E7)
